[[2026-04-13 22:18:20]] {CREATE #10: Define query pipeline data models (schema.py) | QueryIntent (entities, concepts, mnos, releases, query_type, doc_type_scope, standards_refs, likely_features), ScopedQuery, CandidateSet, RetrievedChunk, QueryResponse. All JSON-serializable. }
[[2026-04-13 22:18:22]] {CREATE #11: Build query analyzer (Stage 1) | LLM-driven query analysis: extract entities, concepts, MNO, release, query type, standards refs, likely features. Mock analyzer for keyword-based fallback. Uses LLMProvider Protocol. }
