[[2026-04-13 22:18:27]] {CREATE #14: Build targeted RAG retriever (Stage 4) | Rank candidate chunks by vector similarity with metadata filtering. Diversity enforcement across documents. Uses EmbeddingProvider + VectorStoreProvider. }
[[2026-04-13 22:18:29]] {CREATE #15: Build context assembler (Stage 5) | Assemble LLM prompt from selected chunks + hierarchy paths + standards text + cross-reference annotations. Query-type-specific templates. }
[[2026-04-13 22:18:31]] {CREATE #16: Build LLM synthesizer (Stage 6) | Send assembled context to LLM, generate answer with citations. Query-type-specific system prompts. Uses LLMProvider Protocol. }
